title: Track Finder
description: Fullstack web app that allows runners to locate, look up availability, edit, add, and delete running tracks in their city.

title: Workday Scheduler
description: This is my work day scheduler that allows me to store events, by the hour, for a single day.

title: Senior Travel Covid Care
description: This mobile-first app allows users are able to search for their city and state, physician type, preferred physician gender, and acceptable Covid-risk level for their state.

title: Code Quiz
description: This is a timed quiz that has 5 questions. Once user clicks 'start', all questions are dynamically created through DOM manipulation. Each question has 4 responses that are presented as buttons below the question.

title: Weather Dashboard
description: This is a weather dashboard that displays both the current weather and the 5 day forecast for a selected city.

title: Burger App
description: A fullstack web application that allows users to track burgers that available in a list and then move them to another (devoured) once they are eaten.
